<p class="challenge_1" style="text-align:justify;">Greetings Commander, we have a problem. Last night two of our warp cores were stolen.
We managed to track the warp-path of the thieves as they fled in space. We plotted the
coordinates on this map for you. During the night we followed them on our remaining cores.
We are currently within tracktor distance of the thieves and our status is CLOACKED. We are
capable	of beaming our two warp cores back on board, but the problem is that their shield is
blocking our plan. Can you find the code to deactivate their shield. Good luck on your quest!</p>
